{"tid":2417583,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"是靚午 秦式黃咖喱瀏覽飯 配 雞肉串燒","createTime":"2021-02-22T04:14:55.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-22T13:30:10.000Z","uid":33359,"like":42,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":32,"replies":[{"pid":"caf091afc0b43ec0b4ee5cd83a91d5b65bf689ba","tid":2417583,"uid":33359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-22T04:14:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rWHcy4h.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrWHcy4h.jpg&h=af9047ac&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bB4Kqbh.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbB4Kqbh.jpg&h=6f8ab4e6&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BerHWij.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBerHWij.jpg&h=a86c1fb5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢間鋪我幾次walk in都無位<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n今日終於記得book位<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n講吓味道先<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咖哩好香，落咗唔少椰汁<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n成個口感圓潤咗好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但我覺得偏甜咗少少<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n瀏覽好淋有牛味<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n串燒燒得唔太夠香<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n肉質好嫩<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但個沙嗲我都係覺得偏甜咗少少<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n整體上啲野食幾好味又大份<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n食落幾c伏<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔怪之得walk in永遠都入唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd3c9959bbdb403ec842fe214d2c0db550a91b9e","tid":2417583,"uid":144541,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-22T0